description: A portion of the proceeds from every meal served by the Manna Truck is used by Bethel to help feed the poor throughout Northeast Ohio, and the Manna Truck provides a second chance for men and women who have gone through Lutheran Metropolitan Ministry's culinary training program. By grabbing a meal from the Manna Truck, you are creating jobs for the formerly homeless and helping feed those in need.
name: Manna Food Truck
